		<img src="icon_posticon.gif" border="0" hspace="3"><font color="midnightblue" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="1">Posted&nbsp;-&nbsp;30 Nov 2002&nbsp;:&nbsp; 19:19:33</font>

